title: Year Round Fashionista: Elsa
description: Year Round Fashionista: Elsa is an awesome and cool dress-up game in which you can help choose a variety of outfits for your favorite Disney Frozen princess Elsa! Elsa is not content with only one outfit. She wants to pick her favorite outfit for each month of the year! It is your task to help her pick 12 different outfits together with a matching hairstyle, makeup, and accessories.
